data.description: Discover the charm of this inviting home that offers an open floorplan, an abundance of natural light, crown molding, tile floors throughout, versatile living area, fantastic kitchen with convenient center island, breakfast bar, generous cabinet space, a dedictaed dining area, and the primary bedroom features a full bath. The outdoor space is complete with a covered patio, mature trees and open space for outdoor entertaining and play. Enjoy the added convenience of easy access to major roads, a variety of dining options, shopping destinations, and nearby parks.
